{"tid":1317772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班前線警察係咪未明自己都係祭品之一","createTime":"2019-07-14T22:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T22:42:22.000Z","uid":218313,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"337de3875ff41ccde68b6a0fccae8ca43909c2f6","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:03:46.000Z","msg":"發夢諗到<br />\nDAY 1 開始, <strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府同警察高層已經推緊一局棋</span></strong></strong><br />\n林鄭政府由推&lt;&lt;送中條例&gt;&gt;開始, 一早已經預想到有大型示威會出現<br />\n所以同警察高層開晒會商量應該點應對<br />\n有左&quot;佔中&quot; 既經驗, 佢地想速戰速決<br />\n方法就係將示威標籤做&lt;&lt;暴動&gt;&gt;, 警方就有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">借口</span></span></strong>用較高武力去攪掂示威<br />\n<br />\n所以之後有:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7/6 警車汽油彈</span>  &lt;--想屈示威者已經開始用汽油彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">12/6 二讀示威</span> , 條街出現大量磚頭 <br />\n佢地想要既畫面:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3a5ouij/101p00042po32533nss2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3a5ouij%2F101p00042po32533nss2.jpg&h=d8081425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最終係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無。出。現。到!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後大家都見到, 由於我地行動當時仲好<span style=\"color: blue;\">克制</span>, 出現唔到佢地預想中既畫面<br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span>, 鬼佬指揮官就照劇本升級武力<br />\n催淚彈&gt;橡膠彈&gt;布袋彈 etc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日仍然因為<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (可能班高層根本唔睇新聞, 以為策略好成功)<br />\n就一個二個出黎話定性暴動, 乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n亦即係話, 政府高層/警隊高層, 一早係預左有大量前線警察中磚頭<br />\n俾人圍抽<br />\n中汽油彈<br />\n等<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重受傷機會</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">下制定策略</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">當班前線警察出面俾人鬧<br />\n行出街時又俾街坊趕<br />\n兩邊不是人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>42樓高層就高床軟枕<br />\n洋鬼指揮官又有得升</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真心覺得, 你地咁辛苦係為左乜?</span> </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb5312bc6ea7a424ee7879c04ba187b5e3b9236","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:04:14.000Z","msg":"頂, 想post 講故台, post 錯, sor"},{"pid":"da30fc02a1b26cfc1733cb77d1f7b600c06756bd","tid":1317772,"uid":205505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太唔小心喇"},{"pid":"5d94753079943893b7de53a1d6af8318ca7ea917","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:10:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩又發夢諗<br />\n依幾日示威遊行, 高層咪又係推緊前線警員去做祭品?<br />\n<br />\n可能警員以為自己圍剿緊示威者<br />\n但有無必要咁樣做?<br />\n如果由得示威人士自由散去, 根本乜事都無<br />\n其實, 高層等緊乜野??<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我諗你地心都有答案</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ba543653533dca50fbd270845859ddf03792427","tid":1317772,"uid":102609,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"班狗冇腦<br />\n你咁分析佢哋聽唔明<br />\n只會諗要打死班暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9ecae57d55d4d82cf152e37dfbe2000045699e","tid":1317772,"uid":266578,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"推前線警去硬食林鄭惹落嘅怨氣<br />\n唉真係鄧班前線警員慘<br />\n盧偉聰聰龜縮幾個禮拜，剩係識推班細嘅去死，佢就係冷氣房安坐佢一哥寶座<br />\n到最後林鄭為咗甩身咪要盧偉聰交一堆前線出嚟"},{"pid":"12f305258aab12ee360f23ab581a3ed30a788c7e","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2ba543653533dca50fbd270845859ddf03792427","tid":1317772,"uid":102609,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"班狗冇腦<br />\n你咁分析佢哋聽唔明<br />\n只會諗要打死班暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:32:06.000Z","msg":"有時衝昏頭腦, 抽個身出黎諗下<br />\n就會唔知咁做為左乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己都試過為左某D 野好上心<br />\n但過左之後發現, 原來<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對自己好先係真道理</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d648d720a83cd79d6420cd1891ea30addad40185","tid":1317772,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:40:32.000Z","msg":"on9仔覺得有錢收有人打就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba52c8336ab01eead750228f89456497d771cf1","tid":1317772,"uid":151256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"有腦就唔會去做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9797d326b6489762a2e728bad4531bff075ca47e","tid":1317772,"uid":271223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a542a40cf48749c2b3d1c483ab0aadda60117513","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b9ecae57d55d4d82cf152e37dfbe2000045699e","tid":1317772,"uid":266578,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"推前線警去硬食林鄭惹落嘅怨氣<br />\n唉真係鄧班前線警員慘<br />\n盧偉聰聰龜縮幾個禮拜，剩係識推班細嘅去死，佢就係冷氣房安坐佢一哥寶座<br />\n到最後林鄭為咗甩身咪要盧偉聰交一堆前線出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"無人知依家高層諗緊乜<br />\n上邊D 野始終都係發夢諗出黎<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地咁樣對前線既思維<br />\n即係致佢地人身安全不顧而制定策略<br />\n我覺得真係好不該"},{"pid":"2eed2529d8117df45d4bc5a12ac76e896d882081","tid":1317772,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d648d720a83cd79d6420cd1891ea30addad40185","tid":1317772,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:40:32.000Z","msg":"on9仔覺得有錢收有人打就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"黑社會係咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fce152f634aad67d0b03b2578dd5f6759d144b","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"2eed2529d8117df45d4bc5a12ac76e896d882081","tid":1317772,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d648d720a83cd79d6420cd1891ea30addad40185","tid":1317772,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:40:32.000Z","msg":"on9仔覺得有錢收有人打就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"黑社會係咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講<br />\n我好後生時, 當年好難搵野做<br />\n少不更事都去考過警察<br />\n我過晒D TEST, 到最後遴選面試<br />\n個考官同我講, 你唔好做警察, 做警察SIDE 左你<br />\n<br />\n我好多謝個位女考官<br />\n唔係都無今時今日, <br />\n如果PASS 左, 可能我仲係同班前線警察一樣<br />\n望住班後生仔係咁鬧自己, 唔知為乜<br />\n<br />\n佢地無我咁好彩, 有個&quot;好&quot;既考官<br />\n命運既野過去左係無得揀...<br />\n將來, 仲係自己手中"},{"pid":"ccbf4b9b9c41292f29cb251a33737d565628b4bf","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:02:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩又訓左陣<br />\n發夢諗起張前線警察斷指相<br />\n<br />\n你地以為, 高層一到個張相, 第一個反應會係點?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我幻想</span>, 高層一見到張相, 嘴角笑起上黎<br />\n心諗 :&quot;今日夠料了!&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(以上全部屬幻想及虛構)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5ccbab7d2e1a61eb18af9aa8533ee5d6208f08","tid":1317772,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"警察冇諗到今次香港人唔割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n==================<br />\n不經不覺間，梁烈士過咗身已經一個月，入嚟放低你想對佢講嘅說話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317796</a>"},{"pid":"e7ac396e2a659d06f4b2e72dc314b95a3a51a61d","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:11:07.000Z","msg":"再去訓<br />\n麻煩巴打幫推一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2044e5c3b3b6e76a4bc67ab66decfdb5dfaf7aca","tid":1317772,"uid":67903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:25:26.000Z","msg":"咩呀人地毅進見中學蝦蝦霸霸 出到黎社會又有得做有牌爛仔 又高人工<br />\n<br />\n邊識諗咁多野 <br />\n佢地就係因為唔識思考，唔知趕狗入窮巷既道理，所以造成咁<br />\n<br />\n一個字，唔show number? 下次等絕後啦"},{"pid":"d47acac07eeb18957f57baa87cba867fc9c858a8","tid":1317772,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rtv5fqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtv5fqa.jpg&h=5cbc6d34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"473bdce2dec757c6b324ca2bdf1e05a1a67533dc","tid":1317772,"uid":20723,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hux7tLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHux7tLh.png&h=1a055dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubHLfqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubHLfqh.png&h=fa525c72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8539c805117e8ea79d9a6cfd67e1e7c02122c726","tid":1317772,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:27:19.000Z","msg":"你當啲高層弱智唔睇電視架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"