0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:03:46.000Z","msg":"發夢諗到<br />\nDAY 1 開始, <strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府同警察高層已經推緊一局棋</span></strong></strong><br />\n林鄭政府由推&lt;&lt;送中條例&gt;&gt;開始, 一早已經預想到有大型示威會出現<br />\n所以同警察高層開晒會商量應該點應對<br />\n有左&quot;佔中&quot; 既經驗, 佢地想速戰速決<br />\n方法就係將示威標籤做&lt;&lt;暴動&gt;&gt;, 警方就有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">借口</span></span></strong>用較高武力去攪掂示威<br />\n<br />\n所以之後有:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7/6 警車汽油彈</span>  &lt;--想屈示威者已經開始用汽油彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">12/6 二讀示威</span> , 條街出現大量磚頭 <br />\n佢地想要既畫面:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3a5ouij/101p00042po32533nss2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3a5ouij%2F101p00042po32533nss2.jpg&h=d8081425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最終係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無。出。現。到!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後大家都見到, 由於我地行動當時仲好<span style=\"color: blue;\">克制</span>, 出現唔到佢地預想中既畫面<br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span>, 鬼佬指揮官就照劇本升級武力<br />\n催淚彈&gt;橡膠彈&gt;布袋彈 etc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日仍然因為<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (可能班高層根本唔睇新聞, 以為策略好成功)<br />\n就一個二個出黎話定性暴動, 乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n亦即係話, 政府高層/警隊高層, 一早係預左有大量前線警察中磚頭<br />\n俾人圍抽<br />\n中汽油彈<br />\n等<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重受傷機會</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">下制定策略</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">當班前線警察出面俾人鬧<br />\n行出街時又俾街坊趕<br />\n兩邊不是人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>42樓高層就高床軟枕<br />\n洋鬼指揮官又有得升</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真心覺得, 你地咁辛苦係為左乜?</span> </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"唔好比狗死，重傷點都要救，因為佢地一死，就會有藉口用真槍鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa1d2feee05055eaf2e190f362be74712ba0cf0","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d97882fdaa4227db58d056c007bc2a8ba96a98bc","tid":1317772,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337de3875ff41ccde68b6a0fccae8ca43909c2f6","tid":1317772,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:03:46.000Z","msg":"發夢諗到<br />\nDAY 1 開始, <strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府同警察高層已經推緊一局棋</span></strong></strong><br />\n林鄭政府由推&lt;&lt;送中條例&gt;&gt;開始, 一早已經預想到有大型示威會出現<br />\n所以同警察高層開晒會商量應該點應對<br />\n有左&quot;佔中&quot; 既經驗, 佢地想速戰速決<br />\n方法就係將示威標籤做&lt;&lt;暴動&gt;&gt;, 警方就有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">借口</span></span></strong>用較高武力去攪掂示威<br />\n<br />\n所以之後有:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7/6 警車汽油彈</span>  &lt;--想屈示威者已經開始用汽油彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">12/6 二讀示威</span> , 條街出現大量磚頭 <br />\n佢地想要既畫面:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3a5ouij/101p00042po32533nss2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3a5ouij%2F101p00042po32533nss2.jpg&h=d8081425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最終係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無。出。現。到!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後大家都見到, 由於我地行動當時仲好<span style=\"color: blue;\">克制</span>, 出現唔到佢地預想中既畫面<br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span>, 鬼佬指揮官就照劇本升級武力<br />\n催淚彈&gt;橡膠彈&gt;布袋彈 etc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日仍然因為<span style=\"color: green;\">內部溝通問題</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (可能班高層根本唔睇新聞, 以為策略好成功)<br />\n就一個二個出黎話定性暴動, 乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n亦即係話, 政府高層/警隊高層,